creator: Oxford University Press India
descriptionHtml:
Oxford Areal is an augmented reality app which brings the power of visual search in your hands via an easy-to-use interface.
1. Download the Oxford Areal App.
2. Search for your book.
3. Download the book and scan the full page to play content.

Oxford Areal is a cloud-based app which has unlimited recognition capabilities. Oxford Areal allows you to view animations, videos, interactivities, listen to audio, improve your pronunciation and challenge your knowledge of the subject with multiple activities at your convenience and on your own device. Please note that the app will access your device camera for scanning an image.
